  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/2015_hero/public/2025-09/Rubin%20Marzo%202024%20No37.jpg?itok=Bzn52V6_" width="1600" height="900" alt="NOIRLab observing specialists Carlos Morales (left) and Karla Peña (right) in the Rubin summit control room at Rubin’s mountaintop site of Cerro Pachón, Chile." />





